quran[564]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,Babuzana ngani na
  78,2,Ngezindaba ezinkulu
  78,3,Lezo bona abaphikisana ngazo
  78,4,Lutho! Bayokwazi
  78,5,Lutho! Futhi bayokwazi
  78,6,Asizange yini siwenze umhlaba ube umbhede (indawo yokuphumula) na
  78,7,Kanye nezintaba zaba yizikhonkwane (ezibanjwe umhlaba)
  78,8,Futhi sanidala ngambili (isilisa nesifazane)
  78,9,Futhi sakwenza ukulala kwenu kwaba ukuphumula
  78,10,Futhi sabenza ubusuku babayisembozo
  78,11,Futhisayenzaiminiyabangeyokuhamba(ukuzekusetshenzwe)
  78,12,Futhi sakha phezulu kwenu okuyisikhombisa okuqatha
  78,13,Futhi sabeka isibani esikhanyayo
  78,14,Futhi sehlisela phansi amanzi aphophozayo avela amafini
  78,15,Ukuze siveze ngawo uhlamvu nokumilayo (izihlahla notshani)
  78,16,Kanye nezivande ezinhle
  78,17,Ngempela usuku lokwahlulela yisikhathi esinqunyiwe
  78,18,Usuku okuyoshawa ngalo icilongo bese niyeza niyizixuku
  78,19,Futhi liyovulwa izulu bese kuba yiminyango
  78,20,Futhi izintaba ziyosuswa futhi zibe yinkohliso
  78,21,Futhi isihogo ngasosonke isikhathi silindile
  78,22,(Isihogo) yindawo yokuhlala yabaphula umthetho
  78,23,Bayohlala phakathi kusona ingunaphakade
  78,24,Angeke bazwe phakathi kusona ukubanda futhi angeke (zithole) ukuphuza
  78,25,Ngaphandle kwamanzi abilayo nobovu
  78,26,Umvuzo ofanele
  78,27,Ngempelabonababengakulindeleukubalelwa(ukwehlulelwa)
  78,28,Futhi babewaphika ngempela amavesi kaMvelinqangi
  78,29,Futhi zonke izinto sazibhala encwadini
  78,30,"Ngakho-ke yizwani, manjalo angeke sininezelele ngalutho ngaphandle\tkwesijeziso"
  78,31,Ngempela okwabalungileyo (abamesabayo uMvelinqangi) okwabo yimpumelelo
  78,32,Izivande kanye namagilebhisi
  78,33,Nezintombi ezinhle ezakhiwe kahle ezilinganayo ngeminyaka
  78,34,Nenkomishi echichimayo
  78,35,Lapho phakathi abayizwa inkulumo eyize noma amanga
  78,36,"Umvuzo ovela eNkosini yakho, isipho esibaliwe"
  78,37,"INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba kanye nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili(iNkosi) enomusa, abangakwaziukukhuluma nayo"
  78,38,"Ngosuku lapho uGabriyeli nezingelosi kuyokuma ngabolayini, angeke bakhulume ngaphandle kwalowo ovunyelwe (uMvelinqangi)\tonomusa futhi akhulume okulungile"
  78,39,"Lolo wusuku lwangempela, manjalo noma ngabe ngubani othanda ukuthatha isiphephelo eNkosini yakhe"
  78,40,"Ngempela sanixwayisa ngesijeziso esiseduze, usuku lapho umuntu eyobona lokho okuthunyelwe ngaphambili yizandla zakhe futhi bayothi abangakholwa “Oh ngifisa sengathi ngangiwuthuli”"
  79,1,Ngifunga ngokukhiphayo okucwilisayo
  79,2,Ngifunga ngokukhipha ngobumnene
  79,3,"Ngifunga ngokubhukudayo, ngokubhukuda ngokushesha"
  79,4,Ngifunga ngokuncintisanayo ngokushesha
  79,5,Ngokwenza icebo odabeni
  79,6,Usuku okuyokhala ngalo (icilongo) kunyakaze umhlaba
  79,7,Kuyolandelwa okukhala kwecilongo kwesibili
  79,8,Izinhliziyo ngalolosuku ziyoqhaqhazela
  79,9,Ukubuka kwabo kuyojabhiswa
  79,10,"Bathi, “ngakube ngempela siyobuyiselwa yini esimweni sokuqala (sempilo) na?”"
  79,11,Ngisho noma ngabe sesingamathambo abolile
  79,12,"Bathi,\t“lokho\tkuyokuba\tukuphindela\t(empilweni) enokulahlekelwa"
  79,13,Kuphela kuyokuba ukukhala okukodwa
  79,14,Kulapho bona besemhlabeni
  79,15,Ngakube yafika yini kuwena indaba kaMose
  79,16,Ngenkathi ebizwa yiNkosi yakhe esigodini esingcwele iTuwa
  79,17,(Ithi) hamba uye kuFaro ngempela yena wephule umthetho
  79,18,Bese uthi (kuyena) “ngakube uyafuna yini ukuzihlanza
  79,19,Futhi ngikuholele eNkosini yakho ukuze uyesabe
  79,20,Ngakho-ke wamkhombisa uphawu olukhulu
  79,21,Kepha (uFaro) wenqaba wangahloniphi
  79,22,Wayesephendukela emumva ezabalaza
  79,23,Ngakho-ke waqoqa wamemeza
  79,24,"Wayesethi, “mina ngiyiNkosi yenu ephakeme kakhulu”"
  79,25,"Ngakho-ke wamthatha uMvelinqangi ngesijeziso esiyisibonelo sempilo\tezayo neyamanje"
  79,26,"Ngempela\tkulokho\tkunesifundo\tkulowo\towesaba (uMvelinqangi) olungileyo"
  79,27,Ngakube nina ninzima yini ekudalweni noma yizulu alakhile na
  79,28,Wakuphakamisa ukuphakama kwalo walenza labalihle
  79,29,Futhi wamboza ubusuku balo futhi wakhipha ukukhanya kwalo
  79,30,Nomhlaba emva kwalokho wawendlala
  79,31,Wakhipha kuwona amanzi awo nedlelo lawo
  79,32,Kanye nezintaba wazizinzisa zaqina
  79,33,Injabulo (isabelo) senu kanye nezinkomo zenu
  79,34,Manjalo ngenkathi kufika isehlakalo esikhulu
  79,35,Usuku lapho umuntu ekhumbula konke akuzabalazele
  79,36,Futhi siyovezwa obala isihogo kulowo obonayo
  79,37,Mayelana nalowo owephula umthetho
  79,38,Futhi wakhetha impilo yalomhlaba
  79,39,Ngakho-ke ngempela isihogo sona siyindawo yokuhlala
  79,40,Futhi mayelana nowesaba isimo seNkosi yakhe futhi anqabele umphefumulo (wakhe) ezikhanukweni
  79,41,Ngakho-ke ngempela isivande sona siyindawo yokuhlala
  79,42,Bakubuza ngehora ukuthi liyofika nini
  79,43,Yini wena ongayisho ngalo na
  79,44,YiseNkosini yakho lapho liphelela khona (ulwazi lwalo) ihora
  79,45,Kuphela wena ungumxwayisi kulowo olesabayo
  79,46,Ngosuku abayolibona ngalo (ihora) kuyokuba sengathi bona abazange bahlale (kulomhlaba) ngaphandle kwentambama noma ikuseni kwalo
  80,1,Wahwaqabala wafulathela
  80,2,Ngenxa yokuthi kwafika kuyena impumputhe
  80,3,Futhi yini engakwenza wazi ukuthi angase ahlanzeke
  80,4,Noma akhumbule bese kuyamsiza ukukhumbula
  80,5,Mayelana nalowo obona ukuthi akadingi lutho
  80,6,Manjalo wena uyamnaka
  80,7,Futhi alikho (icala) kuwena uma engahlanzeki
  80,8,Futhi mayelana nalowo owafika kuwena egijima
  80,9,Futhi esaba (uMvelinqangi)
  80,10,Ngakho-ke wena awumnaki
  80,11,Lutho! Ngempela wona (amavesi) ayisikhumbuzo
  80,12,Ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani othandayo akayikhumbule (iQur’an)
  80,13,Emaphepheni (emibhalweni) ehloniphekile
  80,14,Iphakeme ihlanjiwe
  80,15,Ngezandla zababhali (izingelosi)
  80,16,Abahloniphekile abangamanxusa
  80,17,Akubhujiswe umuntu ngenxa yokungakholwa kwakhe
  80,18,Wamdala ngani into
  80,19,"Ngeconsi lesidoda wamdala, manjalo wayeseyamlinganisa (ngokumbumba)"
  80,20,Wayesemenzela lula indlela (yokuzalwa)
  80,21,Wayesemenza ukuthi afe wayesemenzela ingcwaba
  80,22,Bese uma ethanda amvuse ekufeni
  80,23,Lutho! Akakufezi lokho amphoqa ngakho
  80,24,Ngakho-ke umuntu akabheke ekudleni kwakhe
  80,25,Thina sathela amanzi amaningi
  80,26,Sabe sesiqhekeza umhlaba ngokuqhekeka (okukhulu)
  80,27,Sabe sesimilisa kuwona uhlamvu
  80,28,Kanye namagilebhisi nemfino
  80,29,Kanye nomu-olivi nesundu
  80,30,Kanye nezivande ezinothile
  80,31,Nezithelo notshani
  80,32,Yinjabulo (yisabelo) senu kanye nezinkomo zenu
  80,33,"Ngakho-ke\tuma\tkufika\tukukhala\tokunzima\t(usuku lokwahlulelwa)"
  80,34,Usuku lapho umuntu eyobalekela umfowabo
  80,35,Nonina noyise
  80,36,Nonkosikazi wakhe nezingane zakhe
  80,37,Wonke umuntu phakathi kwabo ngalolosuku uyobe ezinake yena
  80,38,Ubuso ngalolosuku buyokhanya
  80,39,"Ukuhleka, ukuthokozela izindaba ezimnandi"
  80,40,Futhi (obunye) ubuso ngalolosuku buyokuba nothuli
  80,41,Ubumnyamabuyobumboza(ubusobomuntuowayengakwenzi okulungileyo)
  80,42,"Labo-ke bona abangakholwa, abonayo abenzi bokungalungile"
  81,1,Khumbula ngenkathi ilanga lisongwa
  81,2,Khumbula nangenkathi izinkanyezi zihlakazeka
  81,3,Khumbula nangenkathi izintaba zisuswa (zibhidlizwa)
  81,4,Khumbula nangenkathi amakameli amithi enganakwa
  81,5,Khumbula nangenkathi izilwane zasendle ezinkulu ziqoqelwa ndawonye
  81,6,Khumbula nangenkathi izilwandle ziba njengemililo evuthayo (zihlangana izilwandle)
  81,7,"Khumbula\tnangenkathi\timiphefumulo\tihlanganiswa nemizimba yayo"
  81,8,"Khumbula\tkanye\tnentombazane\teyangcwatshwa\tiphila ibuzwa"
  81,9,Khumbula ukuthi yabulawelani na
  81,10,Khumbula nangenkathi amakhasi (amaphepha) evulwa
  81,11,Khumbula nangenkathi isibhakabhaka sivulwa
  81,12,Khumbula nangenkathi isihogo senziwa ukuthi sivuthe
  81,13,Khumbula nangenkathi isivande sisondezwa
  81,14,Uyokwazi umphefumulo lokho okuwulethile (izenzo ezinhle noma ezimbi)
  81,15,Ngakho-ke ngifunga ngezinkanyezi
  81,16,Ezihambayo bese ziyacasha
  81,17,Nangobusuku ngenkathi buhamba (kuvela ukukhanya)
  81,18,Nangokusa ngenkathi kukhanya
  81,19,Ngempela kona kuyinkulumo yesithunywa esihloniphekile
  81,20,Umnikazi wamandla kanye nomnikazi wesihlalo sobukhosi osezingeni eliphezulu
  81,21,Usihloniphekile futhi uthembekile (uMuhammad)
  81,22,Futhi umngane wenu akahlanyi
  81,23,Futhi ngempela wambona (uGabriyeli) esemkhathini ocacile
  81,24,Futhi yena akancishani (nolwazi) lokungabonwa
  81,25,Futhi yona (iQur’an) ayisiyona inkulumo kasathane ogxoshiwe (ezulwini)
  81,26,Niyaphi ke
  81,27,Lokhu akuyilutho ngaphandle kwesikhumbuzo semihlaba (sabantu namajinn)
  81,28,Kunoma ngabe ngubani phakathi kwenu othanda ukuqonda
  81,29,Futhi anithandi ngaphandle kokuba kuthanda uMvelinqangi iNkosi yemihlaba (abantu namajinn)
  82,1,Khumbula ngenkathi isibhakabhaka sidabuka phakathi
  82,2,Futhi khumbula angenkathi izinkanyezi ziwa zisakazeka
  82,3,Futhi khumbula nangenkathi izilwandle ziqhuma (izingxenye zazo zihlangana nezinye)
  82,4,Futhi khumbula nangenkathi amangcwaba wmbulwa
  82,5,Umphefumulo uyokwazi lokho owakuthumela ngaphambili nowakushiya ngemumva
  82,6,Oh muntu! Yini eyakukhohlisa ngeNkosi yakho ephanayo
  82,7,"Eyakudala, yakubumba yabe seyiyakulinganisa"
  82,8,Yakwenza waba yinoma yisiphi isimo eyisithandayo
  82,9,Cha! Kepha niyaluphika (usuku) lokwahlulelwa
  82,10,Futhi ngempela kunabaqaphi (izingelosi) phezulu kwenu (ezibhala enikwenzayo)
  82,11,(Abaqaphi) abahloniphekile ababhalayo
  82,12,Bayakwazi lokho enikwenzayo
  82,13,Ngempela abalungile bayobasenjabulweni
  82,14,Futhi ngempela abangalungile bayokuba semlilweni wesihogo
  82,15,Bayongena phakathi kuwona ngosuku lokwahlulela
  82,16,Futhi bona angeke baphuthe kuwona
  82,17,Futhi yini ekwenza wazi ukuthi luyini usuku lokwahlulelwa
  82,18,Khona manjalo yini ekwenza wazi ukuthi luyini usuku lokwahlulelwa
  82,19,Lolo usuku lapho umphefumulo ungeke uphathele (omunye) umphefumulo (amandla okwenza) okuthize futhi umyalo ngalolosuku ngoka Mvelingqangi
  83,1,Usizi kulabo abakhwabanisayo
  83,2,"Labo okuthi uma bethatha isilinganiso kubantu, bathatha ngokugcwele"
  83,3,"Futhi\tuma\tbebalinganisela\tnoma\tbebakalela\tbanikeza okungaphansi (kwesisindo)"
  83,4,Abacabangi yini ukuthi bona bayovuswa kwabafileyo
  83,5,(Bevuselwa) usuku olukhulu
  83,6,Usuku lapho abantu beyokuma ngaphambili kweNkosi yemihlaba
  83,7,Lutho! Ngempela ukubhalwa phansi kwezenzo (zabonayo) kusejele (esimweni esinzima)
  83,8,Futhi yini ekwenza wazi ukuthi yini ijele (isimo esinzima)
  83,9,Incwadi ekubhalwa kuyona (izenzo zabantu) ibhaliwe
  83,10,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  83,11,Labo abaphika usuku lokwahlulelwa
  83,12,Futhi akekho oluphikayo ngaphandle kwawo wonke (umuntu) owephula umthetho oyisoni
  83,13,"Uma\tefundelwa\tamavesi\tethu\tuthi,\t“yizinganekwane zabasendulo”"
  83,14,Lutho! Kepha kunesembozo ezinhliziyweni zabo salokho ababekusebenzela
  83,15,Lutho! Ngempela bona ngalolosuku bayosithezwa (ekuboneni) iNkosi yabo
  83,16,Bese ngempela bona bayongena emlilweni ovuthayo
  83,17,"Bese kuthiwa, “nakhu lokhu nina enanikuphika"
  83,18,Lutho! Ngempela umbhalo (umlando) wabalungile ugciniwe kwi-Illiyun
  83,19,Futhi yini ekwenza wazi ukuthi yini I-illiyun
  83,20,Incwadi elotshiwe
  83,21,Bayoyibona labo abasondele (kuMvelinqangi)
  83,22,Ngempela abalungile basenjabulweni
  83,23,Babheke emibhedeni yokucambalala emihle
  83,24,Uyazi (ngokuzibonela) ebusweni babo ukukhanya kwenjabulo
  83,25,Baphuziswa iwayini elimsulwa elisicilelwe
  83,26,"Isisicilelo\tsalo\tamakha\tfuthi\tkulokho\tabancintisane abancintisani"
  83,27,Inhlanganisela yalo (iwayini) yiTasneem (yisipho sasezulwini esiseqophelweni eliphezulu)
  83,28,"Umthombo\tlapho\tkuphuza\tkhona\tabasondele (kuMvelinqangi)"
  83,29,"Ngempela\tlabo\tababejwayele\tukwenza\tubugebengu babejwayele ukuhleka labo abakholwayo"
  83,30,"Futhi\tkwakuthi\tuma\t(ababenza\tubugebengu)\tbedlula ngakubona bacishelane amehlo"
  83,31,Futhi uma bephindela kubantu babo baphindela benza amahlaya
  83,32,"Futhi uma bebabona babethi, “ngempela laba badukile”"
  83,33,Futhi babengathunyelwanga kubona ukuba ngabalondolozi babo
  83,34,Ngakho-ke ngalolusuku labo abakholwayo bahleka labo abangakholwa
  83,35,Emibhedeni yokucambalala emini bebhekile
  83,36,"Ngakube\tbanikezwa\tumvuzo\tabangakholwa\tngalokho ababekwenza"
  84,1,Khumbula lapho izulu liyohlakazeka khona
  84,2,Futhi khumbula lilalela iNkosi yalo futhi kufanele likwenze lokho
  84,3,Futhi khumbula nangenkathi umhlaba unwetshwa
  84,4,Futhi khumbula (umhlaba) ukhipha konke okuphakathi kuwona usale ungenalutho
  84,5,Futhi ulalela iNkosi yawo futhi kufanele ukwenze lokho
  84,6,Oh muntu! Ngempela wena usebenzele iNkosi yakho ukusebenza okuphelele ekugcineni uzohlangana nayo
  84,7,Mayelana nalowo onikezwa incwadi yakhe (yezenzo zakhe) esandleni sakhe sokunene
  84,8,Manjalo uyokwahlulela ngokwahlulela okulula
  84,9,Futhi aphindele kubantu bakhe ejabulile
  84,10,Kepha lowo onikezwe incwadi yakhe (yezenzo zakhe) ngemumva komhlane wakhe
  84,11,Manjalo uyobe ezifunela ukubhujiswa
  84,12,Futhi angene emlilweni ovuthayo
  84,13,Ngempela yena wayephakathi kwabantu bakhe (bakubo) ejabulile
  84,14,Ngempela yena wayecabanga ukuthi angeke aphindele (kuMvelinqangi)
  84,15,"Yebo!\tNgempela\tiNkosi\tyakhe\tngasosonke\tisikhathi yayimbona"
  84,16,Kepha lutho! Ngifunga ngobubomvu bokushona kwelanga
  84,17,Futhi ngifunga nangobusuku kanye nalokho okwenza ukuthi kubemnyama
  84,18,Futhi ngifunga nangenyanga ngenkathi igcwala
  84,19,Ngempela niyodlula izigaba ngezigaba
  84,20,Ngakho-ke kwenzenjani ngabo ukuthi bangakholwa na
  84,21,Futhi uma befundelwa iQur’an abajabalali (abakhothami kuMvelinqangi)
  84,22,Kepha labo abangakholwanga bayaphika
  84,23,Futhi uMvelinqangi wazi kakhulu ngalokho abakugcina ngaphakathi kubona
  84,24,Ngakho-ke batshele ngesijeziso esibuhlungu
  84,25,Ngaphandle kwalabo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezilungileyo okwabo ngumvuzo ongasoze wanqamuka
  85,1,"Futhi\tngifunga\tngesibhakabhaka\tesibambe\tizinkanyezi ezinkulu"
  85,2,Futhi ngifunga nangosuku oluthenjisiwe
  85,3,Nangofakazi kanye nalokho okufakazelwayo
  85,4,Babhujisiwe (abaqalekiswa) yizihlali zasemseleni
  85,5,Umlilo ogcwele izinkuni
  85,6,Ngenkathi bona bahleli eduzane nawo
  85,7,Futhibonabengofakazikulokhoabakwenzayokwabakholwayo
  85,8,Futhi abazange babahluphe ngaphandle kokuthi abakholelwe kuMvelinqangi ophakeme ngamandla odunyiswayo
  85,9,Lowo okungowakhe umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba futhi uMvelinqangi ungobonwayo (ongufakazi) phezulu kwezinto zonke
  85,10,Ngempela labo abalinga abakholwayo besilisa nabakholwayo besifazane bese bengazisoli (kuMvelinqangi) ngakho-ke okwabo yisijeziso sesihogo futhi okwabo yisijeziso somlilo ovuthayo
  85,11,"Ngempela labo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezilungileyo okwabo yizivande okugeleza ngaphansi kwazo imifula, lokho yimpumelelo enkulu"
  85,12,Ngempela ukushaya kweNkosi yakho kunzima
  85,13,Ngempela iyona eqala (indalo) futhi iyiphinde
  85,14,Futhi yona iyathethelela inothando
  85,15,"Umnikazi\twesihlalo\tsobukhosi,\tAlmajid\t(odunyiswayo ohlonishwayo)"
  85,16,Umenzi walokho akuthandayo
  85,17,Ngakube yafika yini indaba yamabutho empi
  85,18,UFaro kanye noThamud
  85,19,Kepha labo abangakholwanga basekuphikeni
  85,20,Futhi uMvelinqangi ubasingethe ngemumva kwabo
  85,21,Kepha yona iyiQur’an ehloniphekile
  85,22,Esoqwembeni olugciniwe
  86,1,Ngifunga ngesibhakabhaka nangokukhanyayo ebusuku
  86,2,Futhi yini ekwenza wazi ukuthi yini okukhanyayo ebusuku
  86,3,Yinkanyezi ekhanyayo
  86,4,Awukho umphefumulo kepha phezu kwawo kunomlondolozi
  86,5,Ngakho-ke akabheke umuntu ukuthi wadalwa ngani
  86,6,"Wadalwa\tngamanzi\t(uketshezi)\tolukhishwa\t(owesilisa nowesifazane) isidoda"
  86,7,Aphuma phakathi emgogodleni nasezimbanjeni
  86,8,Ngempela yena (uMvelinqangi) uyakwazi ukumphindisela emumva (empilweni)
  86,9,Ngosuku lapho izimfihlo ziyolingwa (ziyovezwa obala)
  86,10,Ngifunga ngakho-ke angeke abenawo amandla nomsizi
  86,11,Futhi ngifunga ngezulu (ngesibhakabhaka) esiletha imvula ngokuphindelela
  86,12,Futhi ngifunga ngomhlaba ngenkathi uqhekeka phakathi
  86,13,Ngempela kona kuyinkulumo ehlukanisayo (okuhle nokubi)
  86,14,Futhi kona akuyiwona umdlalo
  86,15,Ngempela bona benza icebo
  86,16,Futhi nami ngenza icebo
  86,17,"Ngakho-ke\tbanike\tithuba\tabangakholwa,\tbayekwe okwesikhashana ngobumnene"
  87,1,Dumisa igama leNkosi yakho ephakeme kakhulu
  87,2,Okuyiyona eyadala yalinganisa (konke ngesimo sako)
  87,3,Futhi okuyiyona ekalayo futhi eholayo
