  113,5,Kanye nasebubini bonomhawu uma esenomhawu
  114,1,"Yithi, “ngicela isiphephelo ngeNkosi yabantu”"
  114,2,INkosi yesintu
  114,3,UNkulunkulu wesintu
  114,4,Ebubini bomnyenyezi (usathane) uma esehlehlela emumva
  114,5,Lowo onyenyeza ezifubeni zabantu
  114,6,Phakathi kwama-jinn nabantu